lead_paragraph: Rico Gathers scored 14 of his 16 points in the second half to help No. 17 Baylor defeat Oklahoma State 69-65 on Wednesday night.

headline.print_headline: Gathers' Big 2nd Half Leads No. 17 Baylor Past Oklahoma St.
